steps.name: $("By.xpath: //a[@href='/' and contains(@style, 'orange')]") should have(attribute style="color: orange;")
$("By.xpath: //a[@href='/view_cart']/u[text()='View Cart']") should not have([attribute disabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //a[@href='/view_cart']/u[text()='View Cart']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //a[text() = 'Proceed To Checkout']") should not have([attribute disabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //a[text() = 'Proceed To Checkout']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: (//a[@href = '/login'])[2]") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$(".signup-form/button") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //input[@value='Mrs']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$("By.xpath: //button[@data-qa='create-account']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
$(".row b") should have([exact text "Account Created!", 15 s.])
$("By.xpath: //a[@data-qa='continue-button']") should be([clickable: interactable and enabled, 30 s.])
